    <time>2014-08-11T08:50:26Z</time>
    <name>camp a7.6 29/07/2014</name>
    <cmt>SUN festival was amazing. It was difficult to leave that land and the nice people. I'm gonna hang on to this train for a while longer...

On route to Ozora Festival with Adam and Fin (from SUN) Stayed in an actual house! Washed and fed. Thanks Adam. I'll see you in Copenhagen


Hungary: https://vandogtraveller.com/tag/hungary</cmt>
    <desc>SUN festival was amazing. It was difficult to leave that land and the nice people. I'm gonna hang on to this train for a while longer...

On route to Ozora Festival with Adam and Fin (from SUN) Stayed in an actual house! Washed and fed. Thanks Adam. I'll see you in Copenhagen
</desc>
    <sym>Anchor</sym>
    <type>user</type>
