  <wpt lat="46.758458744734526" lon="18.435545498505235">
    <time>2014-08-11T08:54:15Z</time>
    <name>camp a7.7 30/07/2014</name>
    <cmt>Camped outside the entrance to Ozora festival. We tried everything to get in. We spent a day making money busking and selling food. We eventually bought tickets but got them cut off because they were fake. Spent ages getting our money back from the street sellers. We tried to sneak in but got caught and escorted out the area with van still inside. Nearly gave up at 2AM until we met the owner of the whole festival who got us all in for free. The final hurdle was finding a tractor to get the van out the mud. BUT lesson learned; never give up, there is always a way.
Met up with people from SUN and camped with them

Hungary: https://vandogtraveller.com/tag/hungary</cmt>
    <desc>Camped outside the entrance to Ozora festival. We tried everything to get in. We spent a day making money busking and selling food. We eventually bought tickets but got them cut off because they were fake. Spent ages getting our money back from the street sellers. We tried to sneak in but got caught and escorted out the area with van still inside. Nearly gave up at 2AM until we met the owner of the whole festival who got us all in for free. The final hurdle was finding a tractor to get the van out the mud. BUT lesson learned; never give up, there is always a way.
Met up with people from SUN and camped with them</desc>
