    <time>2014-08-11T09:01:41Z</time>
    <name>camp a7.8 5/08/2014</name>
    <cmt>Ozora was incredible. A perfect festival. Went back to Budapest with Adam and Fin. Stayed to Bence and Paula's flat; space gypsie hostel and continued the party. Cheers guys it was real nice


