    <time>2014-08-11T09:37:46Z</time>
    <name>camp a7.9 8/08/2014</name>
    <cmt>Stayed at Adam and Feri's off-grid farm house, right off the beaten track. No electricity or water supply. Eating loads of nice food, cooked on the fire. We played Djembe and guitar all day and night. This is proper off-grid living! you really can live very well for hardly any money at all -- 70Euro a month for 2 people.

Hungary: https://vandogtraveller.com/tag/hungary</cmt>
