    <time>2014-08-11T09:41:18Z</time>
    <name>camp a8.0 11/08/2014</name>
    <cmt>By the river Danube. I'm with Fin and Bea. We washed in the river and hiked the nearby mountains. It got dark and we got lost. We played The Specials and tracks from my childhood through Fin's speaker as we tried to find our way back through the forrest -- It was odd, it was cool.

