    <name>camp c4.9 19/12/2015</name>
    <cmt>Peniche. huge stretch of nice beach. Loads of surfers and kites. The waves are huge. I'm told this is one of the best spots in Europe. Free camping is easy and there are many other vans. Super van friendly!

