    <time>2015-12-26T09:01:59Z</time>
    <name>camp c5.4 24/12/2015</name>
    <cmt>Christmas eve spot. A big lake with nearly full moon in its reflection. No one here and very quiet. Today I met with Chris, a reader of the blog. We did a skydive in the Algarve! woahhh what an experience and in such an amazing location and with such cool people. THANK YOU Chris!

