    <cmt>Merry Christmas! I'm in Morocco. That wasn't the easiest border I've gone through. I will do a post on this. I just realised I don't have maps for Morocco so I stayed the night here in a nice bay/beach area with the big full moon! I need to get to Marrakech for the 29th

